<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>魔法制作 on wdnmlgbd笔记/博客</title><link>https://tencentx.us.kg/categories/%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C/</link><description>Recent content in 魔法制作 on wdnmlgbd笔记/博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-Hans</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 16 Aug 2025 20:05:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://tencentx.us.kg/categories/%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>3-XUI搭建节点</title><link>https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/</link><pubDate>Sat, 16 Aug 2025 20:05:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/cover.png" alt="Featured image of post 3-XUI搭建节点" />&lt;h1 id="3-xui搭建节点">3-XUI搭建节点
&lt;/h1>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>使用最简单的方式搭建一个vless reality节点，而不是为了性能最大化。使用3-xui本身就是为了GUI操作简单&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>本文中的脚本和教程引用了DuangVPS博主发布的教程&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>可选项：&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>BBR开启和选择模式脚本 （我选14：BBR2+FQ）&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget -N --no-check-certificate &amp;#34;https://github.000060000.xyz/tcpx.sh&amp;#34; &amp;amp;&amp;amp; chmod +x tcpx.sh &amp;amp;&amp;amp; ./tcpx.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>运行BBR优化脚本（运行脚本之后先选2再运行选3）&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">bash&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">curl&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">-&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Ls&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">https&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">//&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">github&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">com&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">lanziii&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">bbr&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">-/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">releases&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">download&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">123&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">tools&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">sh&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="第一步安装3x-ui">第一步：安装3x-ui
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>&lt;strong>安装命令&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">bash &amp;lt;(curl -Ls https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mhsanaei/3x-ui/master/install.sh)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>运行脚本后会有如下提示意思是是否需要自定义配置，键入&lt;code>y&lt;/code>然后回车；&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Do you want to continue with the modification y/n?
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>会接连出现如下需要自定义的配置&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Please set up your username: 后面输入要设置的面板用户名
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Please set up your password: 后面输入要设置的面板密码
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Please set up the panel port: 后面输入你要设置的面板端口
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>面板创建完成&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如果需要更改配置如端口号等，在终端输入以下命令即可&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">x-ui
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="第二步进入面板创建节点">第二步：进入面板创建节点
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>&lt;strong>在浏览器地址栏按照如下格式输入面板地址&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">vpsip:端口号/面板路径
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>输入第一步中配置的用户名和密码&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/log.png"
width="929"
height="656"
srcset="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/log_hu_9ff20878725c80f7.png 480w, https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/log_hu_9c06f44e442f003a.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="log"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="141"
data-flex-basis="339px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>可以在这里重新设置你的X-UI的端口和面板&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/set.png"
width="1462"
height="649"
srcset="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/set_hu_fff17efd9077bdf6.png 480w, https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/set_hu_f17549dec3520d4.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="set"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="225"
data-flex-basis="540px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>点击添加入站&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build1.png"
width="692"
height="240"
srcset="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build1_hu_46eff56a4c7679d3.png 480w, https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build1_hu_9209436b684053cb.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="build1"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="288"
data-flex-basis="692px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>然后按照下图直接配置就可以&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>把图二中客户ID中第一个 ‘-’ 前面的自负复制到图三中Dest(Target)中的.com前面去替换掉原来的字符&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build2.png"
width="509"
height="367"
srcset="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build2_hu_882cd831b442303a.png 480w, https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build2_hu_46876259c35f9205.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="build2"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="138"
data-flex-basis="332px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build3.png"
width="509"
height="367"
srcset="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build3_hu_ba6c941700293571.png 480w, https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build3_hu_bf03eefc15ada773.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="build3"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="138"
data-flex-basis="332px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build4.png"
width="486"
height="777"
srcset="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build4_hu_d04306ec15a65184.png 480w, https://tencentx.us.kg/p/vlessbuild1/build4_hu_324c8a7c8ee30ff6.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="build4"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="62"
data-flex-basis="150px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>节点这就搭建好了&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h4 id="第三步将节点添加到clash">第三步：将节点添加到clash
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">proxies:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - name: &amp;#34;节点名称&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> type: vless
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> server: 127.0.0.1 #这里要写节点服务器的公网ip地址
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> port: 25024 #创建节点时设置的端口号
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> uuid: 4357ef26-9987-90jx1a-a5df-2151dacc7020 #这里写图二中的ID
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> network: tcp
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> tls: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> udp: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> flow: xtls-rprx-vision
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> servername: 4287ef26.com # 这里写图二中的Dest(Target)配置的网址
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> reality-opts:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> public-key: FlD9auoJ5TkEydv_mORuZ2SEE6WRGFtTjLz2G1awQXQ #这里写图三中获取的公钥
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> short-id: e6d376d33a5cd40c # 这里写图三中的Short IDs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> client-fingerprint: random # cannot be empty
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>snell节点搭建</title><link>https://tencentx.us.kg/p/snell%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</link><pubDate>Sat, 16 Aug 2025 18:05:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://tencentx.us.kg/p/snell%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://tencentx.us.kg/p/snell%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/cover.jpeg" alt="Featured image of post snell节点搭建" />&lt;h1 id="snell节点搭建">snell节点搭建
&lt;/h1>&lt;p>本文参考了&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&amp;amp;rls=en&amp;amp;q=%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAsnell&amp;amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;amp;oe=UTF-8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>整点猫咪&lt;/a>大佬的文章，并做了一些修改与简化。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>注意：基于debian12，应该适用于debian系列机器。其他发行版需要自己研究基础操作。&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="第一步下载必要软件">第一步：下载必要软件
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo apt update &amp;amp;&amp;amp; sudo apt install wget unzip neovim -y
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果你不是debian系列机器还需要这一步操作：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo dnf install unzip
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="第二部下载snellserver">第二部：下载SnellServer
&lt;/h4>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>文档使用的是snell的最新版本也就是V5，根据你的创建时间和实际需求自行去&lt;a class="link" href="https://kb.nssurge.com/surge-knowledge-base/zh/release-notes/snell" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>官网&lt;/a>查找版本号。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>linux-amd64&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget https://dl.nssurge.com/snell/snell-server-v5.0.0-linux-amd64.zip
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>ARM架构&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget https://dl.nssurge.com/snell/snell-server-v5.0.0-linux-aarch64.zip
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="第三步解压-snell-server-到置顶目录">第三步解压 Snell Server 到置顶目录
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>&lt;strong>linux-amd64&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo unzip snell-server-v5.0.0-linux-amd64.zip -d /usr/local/bin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>ARM架构&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo unzip snell-server-v5.0.0-linux-aarch64.zip -d /usr/local/bin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="第三步操作节点搭建">第三步：操作节点搭建
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>&lt;strong>赋予服务器权限&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">chmod +x /usr/local/bin/snell-server
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>创建配置文件夹&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo mkdir /etc/snell
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>使用Snell的wizard生成一个配置文件&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo snell-server --wizard -c /etc/snell/snell-server.conf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>配置Systemd服务文件&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>编辑snell.serverce文件&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo nvim /lib/systemd/system/snell.service
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>直接把下面的代码复制粘贴进去&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">17
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[Unit]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Description=Snell Proxy Service
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">After=network.target
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[Service]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Type=simple
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">User=nobody
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Group=nogroup
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">LimitNOFILE=32768
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/snell-server -c /etc/snell/snell-server.conf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">AmbientCapabilities=CAP_NET_BIND_SERVICE
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">StandardOutput=syslog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">StandardError=syslog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">SyslogIdentifier=snell-server
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[Install]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">WantedBy=multi-user.target
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>继续执行重载服务&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">sudo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">systemctl&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">daemon&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">-&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">reload&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>配置snell开机自启动&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo systemctl enable snell
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>查看snell状态&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo systemctl status snell
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>执行完以上步骤，并且snell状态没有报错（全绿），那节点就搭建好了&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h4 id="第四步查看snell配置并且在surge中添加">第四步：查看Snell配置，并且在Surge中添加
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>&lt;strong>查看snell配置&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cat /etc/snell/snell-server.conf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>你会得到如下输出：&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[snell-server]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">listen = 0.0.0.0:11807
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">psk = AijHCeos15IvqDZTb1cJMX5GcgZzIVE
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ipv6 = false
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>如果直接在surge的配置文件中添加那么直接写&lt;/strong>：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">节点名称 = snell, XXX.XXX.XXX.XXX, 11807, psk=psk, version=5, tfo=true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>如果要在Surge的GUI中添加那么这样填写&lt;/strong>：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>名称：节点名称&lt;/p>
&lt;p>代理类型：选择SNELL&lt;/p>
&lt;p>服务器地址：填写搭建SNELL服务器的IP地址&lt;/p>
&lt;p>端口号：填写listen那里冒号后面的部分&lt;/p>
&lt;p>psk:填写psk&lt;/p>
&lt;p>协议版本：选择v5&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Obfs：Disabled&lt;/p>
&lt;p>TCP Fast Open：开启&lt;/p>
&lt;p>IPV4&amp;amp;IPV6：双栈&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>